        <definition>bool Dali::WindowDimInfo::isEnabled</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>isEnabled</name>
        <qualifiedname>Dali::WindowDimInfo::isEnabled</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Flag to enable or disable the dimming effect. This is used together with the blur effect. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>When true, the dimming effect is applied to the related region. When false, no dimming is applied and only the blur effect is visible.</para>
<para>Default value: false</para>
<para>@SINCE_2_5.5 </para>
        </detaileddescription>
